greyfox.rxnetwork.internal.strategy.network.predicate

Class RxNetworkInfoPredicate.Type

  • java.lang.Object
    • greyfox.rxnetwork.internal.strategy.network.predicate.RxNetworkInfoPredicate.Type
  • Enclosing class:
    RxNetworkInfoPredicate

    public static final class RxNetworkInfoPredicate.Type
extends java.lang.Object
    Predicate class for filtering reactive streams of RxNetwork by network type.

    Example usage: 

    
 rxnetwork.observe()
          .subscribeOn(Schedulers.io())
          .filter(hasType(TYPE_WIFI, TYPE_MOBILE))
          .observeOn(AndroidSchedulers.mainThread())
          .subscribe(...);
